It would be the common multiple of all the bodies' orbital and rotational periods. It's an N-system of equations of the form:

P1 x a = X

P2 x b = X

P3 x c = X

...

Where P1,P2,P3,... are the periods in question and the values a,b,c... are constrained to be integers. X is the total period time.
